summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; amending Chapter 23.32 of the Seattle Municipal Code at page 15 of the Official Land Use Map, to rezone property located at 2140 N 113th St., from Single Family 7200 (SF 7200) to Lowrise 1 (L1) multifamily residential and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of Howland Homes L.L.C., C.F. 307285, Project Number 2500126)
